{"categories":["newsletter","beauty-cosmetics","e-commerce"],"collections":"","description":"Unlock the secret to flawless skin with our exclusive beauty and personal care newsletter. Perfect for e-commerce shoppers, our curated content offers expert skincare advice, personalized recommendations, and exclusive deals on top beauty products. Discover the latest skincare trends, learn about innovative beauty technologies, and explore the best practices for a radiant, healthy complexion. Our newsletter also features exclusive discounts on premium beauty and personal care products, making it easier than ever to achieve your skincare goals. Whether you're looking for acne solutions, anti-aging remedies, or simply wish to pamper your skin, our newsletter is your ultimate guide to achieving your dream skin. Subscribe now and embark on your journey to a more confident and beautiful you.","short_description":"Discover flawless skin with our beauty and personal care newsletter. Get expert skincare advice, personalized recommendations, exclusive e-commerce deals on top beauty products, and more. Subscribe for skincare solutions, anti-aging remedies, and exclusive discounts. Your journey to dream skin starts here.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Screenshot_2022-08-16_at_1.10.20_PM.png","description":"Versatile graphic and web designer with 8+ years of experience in tech, e-commerce and fashion industries. Bookworm, novice coder, and always up for a challenge!","short_description":"","display_name":"Seanei Gibbons","id":"seanei-gibbons"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n\t<title></title>\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o